- [ ] Provide clear visual hierarchy with typography and spacing
- [ ] Include helpful microcopy and inline assistance
- [ ] Show clear feedback for all user actions
- [ ] Work efficiently on mobile devices with touch-friendly targets
- [ ] Support keyboard navigation with visible focus states
